import React from 'react'
import { Grid } from 'semantic-ui-react'
import ProfileHeader from './ProfileHeader'
import { ProfileContent } from './ProfileContent'

export const ProfilePage = () => {
    return (
        <Grid>
            <Grid.Column width={16}>
                <ProfileHeader />
                <ProfileContent/>
            </Grid.Column>
            
        </Grid>
    )
}
